{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Shopify Propaganda Poster","content":"<html><head></head><body><p>At Shopify, we have &#x201C;design challenges&#x201D; every now and then. This week&#x2019;s challenge was to create a propaganda poster. Below is the poster that I designed, I&#x2019;m pretty proud of it &#x1F642; </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/static/9259c8d9de1506b53847644c36d1b6ba/a296c/shopify_propaganda.jpg\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 650px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 129.375%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n    <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image alignnone size-medium wp-image-1709\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Shopify Propaganda\" title=\"shopify_propaganda\" src=\"/static/9259c8d9de1506b53847644c36d1b6ba/a111b/shopify_propaganda.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/9259c8d9de1506b53847644c36d1b6ba/aca85/shopify_propaganda.jpg 163w,\n/static/9259c8d9de1506b53847644c36d1b6ba/0954f/shopify_propaganda.jpg 325w,\n/static/9259c8d9de1506b53847644c36d1b6ba/a111b/shopify_propaganda.jpg 650w,\n/static/9259c8d9de1506b53847644c36d1b6ba/a296c/shopify_propaganda.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\">\n  </span></a></p>\n<div class=\"sub\">Shopify Propaganda Poster</div>\n<p> <!--more--> </p>\n<h3>Inspiration:</h3>\n<p>I looked at a lot of American posters from World War II for inspiration. I&#x2019;ve always loved propaganda posters, especially how they make everything sound really imperative. I also liked how they mixed sans-serif fonts with script fonts.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"https://www.tetchi.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/Get-Hot-Keep-Moving1.jpeg\" alt title=\"Get Hot - Keep Moving\" width=\"237\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1716\"></p>\n<div class=\"sub\">One of my inspirations</div>\n<p>Overall I think I was able to pull off a pretty legit-looking propaganda poster. It was a good exercise for learning blend modes as well. </p>\n<p>THE END</p>\n</body></html>"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"shopify-propaganda-poster"}}